Privacy Policy

Last updated: 10 September, 2024

This privacy policy governs your use of the "Funny Ringtones" mobile application (hereafter referred to as "the App"). We are committed to protecting your privacy and providing a safe user experience.

1. Data Collection
We do not collect any personal or non-personal information from users. The App is designed to function without requiring any personally identifiable information (PII).

2. Third-Party Services
The App uses Google AdMob for advertising purposes. AdMob may collect certain information to display personalized ads, including device information, location, and usage data. This information is collected and processed by AdMob, and we do not have access to it.

For more information on how AdMob handles your data, please review Google's Privacy Policy.

3. Permissions
The App may request access to:

Storage: To save ringtones to your device. This permission is used solely for the functionality of the app and not for any data collection purposes.
4. Data Usage
As mentioned, we do not collect or store any data from users. Any data collected through third-party services like AdMob is used only for advertising purposes as outlined in their respective privacy policies.

5. Data Sharing
We do not share, sell, or rent any personal information, as we do not collect it. However, third-party services like AdMob may share data in accordance with their privacy policies.

6. Security
Although we do not collect any personal data, we take reasonable measures to protect the integrity of the app and ensure a safe user experience.

7. Childrenâ€™s Privacy
The App is not intended for children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect data from children. If you believe we have inadvertently collected information from a child under 13, please contact us so we can remove the information.

8. Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected with the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. It is recommended to review this policy periodically.

9. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, feel free to contact us at betapixel92@gail.com.
